external_knowledge:
- 'versatile' refers to text editors that are extensible;
- 'typical cost' refers to the average price of the text editors under the 'Standard' price type;
- 'more than five entries' means editors must have more than five records in the database.

sql:
SELECT editor_id, COUNT(extension_id) AS number_of_extensions
FROM extensions
GROUP BY editor_id;

external_knowledge:
- Average rating is calculated as the mean of all ratings for each editor;
- The total reviews and total helpfulness votes are cumulative metrics collected across all editors from each vendor;
- The query aims to showcase which vendors have the most positively reviewed text editors.

sql:
SELECT editor_name, price
FROM editors
ORDER BY price DESC;
